[normal]o this parliamentary inquiry i
[normal]n
[normal]to h
[normal]eat.
[normal]The UKDEA believes that the inquiry
[normal] (through the examination of stakeholder views)
[normal] will lead to further understanding of
[normal] 
[normal]the key
[normal] 
[normal]as
[normal]pects to heat, which
[normal] are:
[normal]As one of the
[normal] 
[normal]UKDE
[normal]A’s primary commitments relates to
[normal] ena
[normal]bling the 
[normal]greater use of district energy where this
[normal] is beneficial
[normal], we have 
[normal]provided responses
[normal] to parts of the inquiry we felt
[normal] were
[normal] mos
[normal]t relevant to district
[normal]/community
[normal] en
[normal]e
[normal]rgy.
[normal] 
